"     Marisa Klein-Gitelman, MD, MPH",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"    <a class=\"contributor contributor_credentials\" href=\"UTD.htm?15/51/16183/contributors\">",
"     Sheldon L Kaplan, MD",
"    </a>",
"    <br/>",
"   </div>",
"   <div>",
